, and myocardial contractility.  Patients should have cardiovascular and respiratory vital signs and state of consciousness constantly monitored while under treatment.', 'Synergism', 'Additional use of local anesthetics should generally be avoided within 96 hours following administration of bupivacaine.', NULL, NULL, 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic');
